A CONVICTED sex offender has been found guilty of rape, indecent assault and abduction charges.Calan Morrison, 29, raped one woman at houses in Fernhill, Glasgow, and at Galston, East Ayrshire.He indecently assaulted another victim at houses in Elderslie, Renfrewshire, and Clydebank, West Dunbartonshire.He also abducted two women who were left locked in a flat in Faifley, Clydebank.Sentence on Morrison was deferred and he was remanded in custody.Morrison, who has a previous conviction for sex with an underage girl, was also placed on the sex offenders' register.